    "In 1911 his work on <em>Ulmer Plastik um 1500</em>, caught the attention of the scholars <a href=\"/clemenp\">Paul Clemen</a>, <a href=\"/falkej\">Jakob Falke</a> and Philipp Halm (1854-1923) at the Technische Hochschule.": [],
    "He taught art history there until 1924.": [],
