    "Jahrhunderts</em> (1931).": [],
    "In 1924 Baum was called to be the director of the museum at Ulm.": [],
    "There he dedicated himself to the history of local art and artists.": [],
    "He married Emma Gruner (1893-1970), a protestant woman, in 1929.": [
